<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>How to Use - Food Donation</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/common.css" />
    <style>
      body { font-family: Poppins, sans-serif; padding: 20px; background: #f7fafc; }
      .guide-wrap { max-width: 1000px; margin: 28px auto; }
      .guide-hero { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.06); margin-bottom: 18px }
      .guide-title { font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight:700; margin-bottom:6px }
      .guide-sub { color: #6b7280; margin-bottom: 8px }
      .steps { display:grid; gap:12px; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px,1fr)); }
      .step { background:#fff; padding:14px; border-radius:10px; box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.04) }
      .step h3 { margin:0 0 6px 0 }
      .back { display:inline-block; margin-top:12px; text-decoration:none; color:#0f172a }
      @media (max-width:480px) { .guide-wrap { padding:12px } .guide-title{ font-size:1.25rem } }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="guide-wrap">
      <div class="guide-hero">
        <div class="guide-title">How to Use This App</div>
        <div class="guide-sub">A short walkthrough to help Donors and Organizations use the platform effectively.</div>
        <a class="back" href="/">← Back to Home</a>
      </div>

      <div class="steps">
        <div class="step">
          <h3>How to Use This App</h3>
          <p><strong>Overview</strong></p>
          <p>This platform connects donors with organizations to reduce food wastage and help people in need. There are two types of users: Donors and Organizations.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <h3>For Donors</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Register</strong> — Sign up as a donor using your personal details and create a strong password.</li>
            <li><strong>Login</strong> — Login using your registered email and password.</li>
            <li><strong>Donate Food or Grocery</strong> — Choose an organization, enter item details and quantity, then submit the donation.</li>
            <li><strong>Track Donation</strong> — View donation status in Donation History: Pending, Accepted, Collected, or Rejected.</li>
            <li><strong>Notifications</strong> — Receive updates when your donation is accepted, collected, or rejected.</li>
            <li><strong>Profile</strong> — View your details and total donations made.</li>
            <li><strong>Forgot Password</strong> — Reset your password using the email-based reset option.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="step">
          <h3>For Organizations</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><strong>Register</strong> — Register your organization with valid details and an Organization ID.</li>
            <li><strong>Login</strong> — Login using email, password, and Organization ID.</li>
            <li><strong>View Donation Requests</strong> — Donation requests appear in the History section.</li>
            <li><strong>Accept or Reject Donations</strong> — Organizations can accept or reject donation requests from the History section.</li>
            <li><strong>Further Actions</strong> — After accepting or rejecting a donation, go to the History page to perform further actions such as marking donations as collected.</li>
            <li><strong>Notifications</strong> — Receive alerts for new donation requests and status updates.</li>
            <li><strong>Profile</strong> — View organization details and donation history.</li>
            <li><strong>Logout</strong> — Use the Logout option to securely exit the application.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
